news.news: Agbaji will head to the bench for Monday's game against the Bucks.
news.analysis: With the Raptors back to full strength Monday, Agbaji will revert to the second unit. In two appearances off the bench this year, Agbaji is averaging 12.5 points, 5.0 rebounds, 1.5 assists and 1.5 blocks in 28.7 minutes.
